{"tid":2028853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「移民台灣」　搜尋量一夜爆增4倍","createTime":"2020-05-22T04:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T06:38:49.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3ac8e1cf6a2681b3e3711ba2da3f377ac91a9b3a","tid":2028853,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T04:08:31.000Z","msg":"中國在昨（21）公布全國人大會議議程，將會審議「港版國安法」，將中國的國家安全法納入香港《基本法》附件三當中，成為香港的「全國性法律」，這就相當於直接繞過香港立法，摧毀一國兩制的最重要精神，外界形容是「直接兌現一國一制」。這讓香港人陷入恐慌，香港地區的Google關鍵字「移民」、「台灣」，在21日晚間時暴增到平日的四倍以上。<br />\n<br />\n中共官媒《人民日報》則是發表評論表示，絕不容許香港成為國家安全的短板，並強調「勢在必行」。香港學運領袖、香港眾志創黨主席羅冠聰對此表示，「我們需要最強的意志，來面對最黑暗的世代。我們不可就此放棄。來吧，香港人不好戰；但要戰，就戰」，而這一切也讓香港人恐慌，查詢香港地區的Google搜尋關鍵字，可以發現21日晚間的「移民」、「台灣」次數暴增，是原本的四倍以上，即使深夜也是平日的兩倍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/22/2568063-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F22%2F2568063-PH.jpg&h=1dd0600e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=747448\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D747448&d=ppuFFh6piFuOrul45s7BzZKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=b0e6a54a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D747448&h=25a4b16c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=747448</a>"},{"pid":"994a7acc00e0a4570369dbfc576ee04ddfa3e566","tid":2028853,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:27:18.000Z","msg":"遲下中共武統台灣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n準備迎接二次回歸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9340d6a88213998880034a0f51e1b565c430913e","tid":2028853,"uid":14918,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:28:55.000Z","msg":"香港人：我討厭政治<br />\n國安法<br />\n<br />\n香港人：移民台灣"},{"pid":"87610d85aaa84f6c3e767397a9c9029c0f219537","